533, \"to\": 7544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the team in Paris is the largest while also having its own emblem.\", \"from\": 7547, \"to\": 7617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7564, \"end\": 7569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.642087607092171e-27, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 7551, \"to\": 7559}, {\"ngram\": \"its own emblem\", \"from\": 7602, \"to\": 7616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It matters 100%,\\\" Ngamba said of the emblem.\", \"from\": 7619, \"to\": 7664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7639, \"end\": 7645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\", \"score\": 0.9845467322481923, \"rank\": 0.01569581945247986, \"text\": \"Ngamba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100%\", \"from\": 7631, \"to\": 7635}, {\"ngram\": \"the emblem\", \"from\": 7653, \"to\": 7663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The foundation is about the team, about a family.\", \"from\": 7665, \"to\": 7715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The foundation\", \"from\": 7666, \"to\": 7680}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 7690, \"to\": 7698}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 7706, \"to\": 7714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being part of the unique family is what it is all about.\", \"from\": 7716, \"to\": 7772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 7722, \"to\": 7726}, {\"ngram\": \"the unique family\", \"from\": 7730, \"to\": 7747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We competed individually in the past, or 2-3 of us.\", \"from\": 7774, \"to\": 7826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 7803, \"to\": 7811}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7823, \"to\": 7825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now we are a big group, a family going out there to represent the refugee team.\", \"from\": 7827, \"to\": 7906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big group\", \"from\": 7838, \"to\": 7849}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 7851, \"to\": 7859}, {\"ngram\": \"the refugee team\", \"from\": 7889, \"to\": 7905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will hold our head high and be proud of the team we are part of.\", \"from\": 7907, \"to\": 7974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our head\", \"from\": 7920, \"to\": 7928}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 7950, \"to\": 7958}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 7966, \"to\": 7970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It shows we are not just refugees, we are athletes.\", \"from\": 7976, \"to\": 8028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just refugees\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8010}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 8019, \"to\": 8027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(People) see us as refugees but forget we are athletes with the same goals as the other countries represented here.\", \"from\": 8029, \"to\": 8144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(People\", \"from\": 8029, \"to\": 8036}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8042, \"to\": 8044}, {\"ngram\": \"refugees\", \"from\": 8048, \"to\": 8056}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 8075, \"to\": 8083}, {\"ngram\": \"the same goals\", \"from\": 8089, \"to\": 8103}, {\"ngram\": \"the other countries\", \"from\": 8107, \"to\": 8126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can achieve the same thing, win the same thing, have the same drive, the same hunger and the same energy.\\\"\", \"from\": 8145, \"to\": 8254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 8160, \"to\": 8174}, {\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 8180, \"to\": 8194}, {\"ngram\": \"the same drive\", \"from\": 8201, \"to\": 8215}, {\"ngram\": \"the same hunger\", \"from\": 8217, \"to\": 8232}, {\"ngram\": \"the same energy\", \"from\": 8237, \"to\": 8252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For co-flagbearer Yahya Al Ghotany, who was forced to leave war-torn Syria and will compete in taekwondo, the team was sending a message of hope.\", \"from\": 8256, \"to\": 8401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8275, \"end\": 8280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_the_Baptist\", \"score\": 0.9999999999627107, \"rank\": 3.693608046192771e-11, \"text\": \"Yahya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_the_Baptist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_the_Baptist\"}, {\"begin\": 8326, \"end\": 8331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\", \"score\": 0.9538245252648654, \"rank\": 0.048410869592181764, \"text\": \"Syria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"taekwondo\", \"from\": 8351, \"to\": 8360}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 8362, \"to\": 8370}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 8383, \"to\": 8392}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 8396, \"to\": 8400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Ghotany only picked up the sport once he was at a refugee camp in Jordan.\", \"from\": 8402, \"to\": 8478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8472, \"end\": 8478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999999473666334, \"rank\": 5.165806894287778e-08, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Al Ghotany\", \"from\": 8402, \"to\": 8412}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 8428, \"to\": 8437}, {\"ngram\": \"a refugee camp\", \"from\": 8453, \"to\": 8467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a wonderful feeling knowing I am representing many people who have gone through the same experience as me, just like me,\\\" he told Reuters.\", \"from\": 8480, \"to\": 8625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 86